" /></blockquote><br />\n資本主義係咁架啦，關中唔中國咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b59c9b6478e75b337db486b4fd15d65b4ea5f28","tid":118071,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05dOpAO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05dOpAO.jpg&h=45c75693&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n人工智慧恥笑緊我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}